    "# Stokes + Jones\n",
    "S1 = Stokes('S1 incoherent')\n",
    "M1 = np.array([1, 1, 0, 0])\n",
    "S1.from_matrix(M1)\n",
    "E1 = Jones_vector()\n",
    "M2 = np.array([[0], [1]])\n",
    "E1.from_matrix(M2)\n",
    "print(S1+E1)\n",
    "S1.name = 'S1 coherent'\n",
    "S1.global_phase = 0\n",
    "print(S1+E1)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "S1 = Stokes('S1 incoherent')\n",
    "M1 = np.array([[1, 0, 1, 0], [1, 1, 0, 0]])\n",
    "S1.from_matrix(M1)\n",
    "E1 = Jones_vector()\n",
    "M2 = np.array([[1], [1j]])\n",
    "E1.from_matrix(M2)\n",
    "print(S1+E1)\n",
    "S1.name = 'S1 coherent'\n",
    "S1.global_phase = 0\n",
    "print(S1+E1)\n",
    "\n",

    "M1 = np.array([[1, 0, 1, 0], [1, 1, 0, 0]])\n",
    "S1.from_matrix(M1)\n",
    "E1 = Jones_vector()\n",
    "M2 = np.array([[1], [1j]])\n",
    "E1.from_matrix(M2)\n",
    "print(S1-E1)\n",
    "S1.name = 'S1 coherent'\n",
    "S1.global_phase = 0\n",
    "print(S1+E1)\n"
